System Architecture for Laundry Connect App

OVERVIEW 
Laundry Connect is an on-demand platform that connects users to laundry women in their area. Users can schedule pickups, track progress, and make secure payments â€” all in one place.

Architecture Components
1. Frontend
- User-friendly interface for customers and service providers
- Technologies: React.js (Web), React Native (Mobile)
- Key features:
  - User login/signup
  - Order placement and tracking
